---
import Divider from "../components/ui/Divider.astro";
import Prose from "../components/ui/Prose.astro";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About — avrdu.de">
  <div class="about-page">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>

    <Divider />

    <Prose>
      <p>I'm a developer who builds things for the web. I like simple tools, fast sites, and writing things down so I don't forget them later.</p>

      <p>This site is where I put posts, TILs, and project notes. It's built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, ships zero client JavaScript, and is deployed on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare Pages</a>. I used AI to help build it because I'm hopeless at design. I can write code all day but ask me to pick a font pairing and I'll stare at the screen for three hours and end up with Comic Sans.</p>

      <p>If something on this site is broken, there's a nonzero chance it was generated by an AI that hallucinated the fix. <a href="/posts/hello-world/">I wrote about that.</a></p>

      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/avr6ude">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/avrdude/">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://t.me/avrdudec">Telegram</a></li>
      </ul>
    </Prose>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-xl);
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
</style>
